00:16:06,487 --> 00:16:07,836
the house of representatives'

244
00:16:07,967 --> 00:16:09,838
unamerican activities
committee.

245
00:16:09,969 --> 00:16:11,883
Among the well informed
witnesses testifying

246
00:16:11,971 --> 00:16:13,537
is j. Edgar hoover,

247
00:16:13,668 --> 00:16:16,018
head of the federal bureau
of investigation.

248
00:16:16,149 --> 00:16:18,803
Mr. Hoover speaks with
authority on the subject.

249
00:16:18,890 --> 00:16:20,980
The communist party
of the United States

250
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:24,200
is a fifth column
if there ever was one.

251
00:16:24,287 --> 00:16:26,289
It is far better
organized than were

252
00:16:26,376 --> 00:16:30,859
the Nazis in occupied countries
prior to their capitulation.

253
00:16:30,946 --> 00:16:33,035
They are seeking
to weaken america,

254
00:16:33,166 --> 00:16:36,430
just as they did
in their era of obstruction,

255
00:16:36,560 --> 00:16:38,345
when they were aligned
with the Nazis.

256
00:16:38,475 --> 00:16:42,218
Their goal is the overthrow
of our government.

257
00:16:42,349 --> 00:16:47,049
There is no doubt as to where a
real communist's loyalty rests.

258
00:16:47,180 --> 00:16:50,226
Their allegiance is to Russia,
not the United States.

259
00:16:50,357 --> 00:16:52,620
The reason that robeson
was a very strong supporter

260
00:16:52,750 --> 00:16:54,839
of the Soviet union was,

261
00:16:54,970 --> 00:16:59,322
